data.analysis: Based on the console logs, this is a comprehensive analysis of Houston's top 3 startup accelerators and their comparative strengths. The analysis was generated through Perplexity AI's sonar-pro model with real-time data integration from Google Places API and OpenStreetMap data sources. The response includes detailed insights about Station Houston, Rice Alliance, and Houston Technology Center, along with their geographic distribution, program offerings, and competitive positioning within the Texas startup ecosystem.
